{"tid":1857333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"護士朋友都講真係要買定糧食,第一波無知道幾嚴重,隨時無物流要停工","createTime":"2020-02-02T06:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T12:52:37.000Z","uid":179775,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"dbef732698297a511fd2c469cd47ae0ad017aec5","tid":1857333,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T06:42:51.000Z","msg":"佢話未開始已經停工<br />\n一爆你唔通叫人返工呀"},{"pid":"db0e68f8e5ae7eb874edb12e0bff8cd5d13ddfc6","tid":1857333,"uid":189638,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T06:50:18.000Z","msg":"無錯，如果香港被宣傳作為疫區，真係連貨船都唔嚟香港，進出香港要消毒，仲邊有船嚟。<br />\n<br />\n再被其他國家禁飛，走又走唔到。<br />\n<br />\n如果情況許可，真心建議暫時去外國遠離人煙嘅地方避下，等情況好轉先返香港。<br />\n<br />\n香港一日唔封關，個情況唔知會惡化成點<br />\n連登一早就知武漢肺炎，但好多人都係未做好充足嘅預防，買唔夠口罩，消毒藥水<br />\n<br />\n情況許可，真係唔好賭香港嘅疫情會變成點。<br />\n柒婆2個仆街仔冇一個係香港，再睇下啲仆街高官嘅屋企人，有幾多個留係香港？<br />\n<br />\n柒婆一心攬炒，一心諗引爆肺炎"},{"pid":"876528b2a031ae05b5335169039515b7b87c9896","tid":1857333,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T06:53:38.000Z","msg":"沙士都未變疫埠"},{"pid":"8aebe4cd76ef8c5753befe2deb94dd4b67a663b2","tid":1857333,"uid":179775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"876528b2a031ae05b5335169039515b7b87c9896","tid":1857333,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T06:53:38.000Z","msg":"沙士都未變疫埠"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T06:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嚴重過沙士啦"},{"pid":"6ef34ceada22b5f823b2f48f2ff6b20ebf432df4","tid":1857333,"uid":28833,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T06:59:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5f677a91939247256e8a8db8ae57ed200bddc71","tid":1857333,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ef34ceada22b5f823b2f48f2ff6b20ebf432df4","tid":1857333,"uid":28833,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8aebe4cd76ef8c5753befe